productReviews.reviewText: heard about this on rebetiko radio, decided to give it a try.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
My co-worker Mitchell has one of these. He says it looks dry.
This Frozen works quite well. It pointedly improves my golf by a lot.
I saw one of these in Canada and I bought one.
